snippet.title: Amber ; genshin impact playlist
snippet.description:
ThunderEasy on Reddit (atleast I think so) 

I am very sorry. Some of the viewers didn’t like my “genshin impact playlist with their taste of music” I have read some comments saying “it doesn’t match with their personalities” or “this playlist sucks have you ever played genshin?” I am sorry if it offended or you just don’t have taste of music, listen bitch if you don’t like it just mind your god damn business and not comment at all, lmao do you think I care? Besides no one asked. If you don’t like it no need to tell me, because I understand that you don’t have the greatest taste as a legend like me. “These are just popular tiktok songs.” Oh well I’m sorry, What was I supposed to do, not put popular tiktok songs? Almost every song in the internet is on tiktok 😒 So what did we learn today person with no music taste? Mind your own fucking business, no one cares so shut up. 



Anyways.

Hellooo!! I made a new account on Instagram so please follow it if you want to (⊃｡•́‿•̀｡)⊃ 
Username: hrrhve
________________________________________________________________________________________________
Dm me if you have any requests I will be always their to take some if I have time (• ◡•)
______________________________________________________________________________________
I do not own of these song's (no shit) so please check the original artists! ~(˘▾˘~)
_________________________________________________________________________________________________

Link of my playlists will be here☟︎
